comment: Flash only if I’m allowed to start using my shoulder.
Honestly﹐ this is probably the best V1 in the gym. It has the essence of climbing.
Went straght up to the undercling from the start﹐ skipping two holds on right. I skipped several holds after that﹐ but it still is a nice route with a fun topout.
Moonboardish fnger intensive route. Locked off with the far right foot to the finish.
